description: This file contains functions to build SOAP request messages for various CCSP CWMP protocol operations, such as GetRPCMethods, Inform, TransferComplete, Kicked, RequestDownload, AutonomousTransferComplete, etc. It involves creating XML DOM nodes, setting attributes, and encoding them into SOAP messages, indicating it is a source implementation for building SOAP requests for CWMP protocol.
